oxnews.com/world/2015/03/26/saudi-arabia-launches-airstrikes-in-yemen-targeting-rebel-held-military.html|agency=[[Associated Press]]|title=Saudi Arabia launches airstrikes in Yemen, targeting rebel-held military installations|last=Al-Haj|first=Ahmed|date=26 March 2015|accessdate=4 April 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Child soldiers from Darfur fighting at front line of war in Yemen, returned soldiers say |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/child-soldiers-yemen-war-sudan-saudi-arabia-darfur-poor-front-line-deaths-janjaweed-a8703186.html |work=The Independent |date=29 December 2018}}</ref><br />\n{{flag|UAE}}<br />{{flag|Bahrain}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{flag|Kuwait}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{flag|Qatar}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{small|(until 5 June 2017)}}<br />{{flag|Jordan}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{flag|Djibouti}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{flag|Egypt}}<ref name=\"offensive\"/><br />{{flag|Senegal}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/04/us-yemen-saudi-senegal-idUSKBN0NP1N920150504|agency=Reuters|title=Senegal to send 2,100 troops to join Saudi-led alliance|date=4 May 2015|accessdate=4 May 2015}}</ref><br />{{flag|United States}}<ref>{{cite news |title=US special forces secretly deployed to assist Saudi Arabia in Yemen conflict |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/us-special-forces-saudi-arabia-yemen-war-green-berets-houthi-rebels-mohammed-bin-salman-a8335481.html |work=The Independent |date=3 May 2018}}</ref><ref>\"[https://theintercept.com/2017/11/20/60-minutes-yemen-war-us-involvement/ In Yemen's \"60 minutes\" moment, no mention that the U.S. is fueling the conflict]\". ''[[The Intercept]].'' 20 November 2017.</ref><br />[[File:ShababFlag.svg|22px|border]] [[al-Qaeda in the Arabian Peninsula|Al-Qaeda]]<ref name=\"al-Qaeda\">{{cite news |title=Report: Saudi-UAE coalition 'cut deals' with al-Qaeda in Yemen |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2018/08/report-saudi-uae-coalition-cut-deals-al-qaeda-yemen-180806074659521.html |work=Al-Jazeera |date=6 August 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=US allies, Al Qaeda battle rebels in Yemen |url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2018/08/07/unite-with-devil-yemen-war-binds-us-allies-al-qaida.html |publisher=Fox News |date=7 August 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Allies cut deals with al Qaeda in Yemen to serve larger fight with Iran |url=https://www.sfgate.com/world/article/Allies-cut-deals-with-al-Qaeda-in-Yemen-to-serve-13135822.php |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=6 August 2018}}</ref> \n{{collapsible list\n| title = <small>Support:</small>\n| {{flag|Somalia|size=20px}}<ref name=\"Ssfpstsciy\">{{cite news|title=SOMALIA: Somalia finally pledges support to Saudi-led coalition in Yemen \u2013 Raxanreeb Online |url=http://www.wargeyska.so/somalia-somalia-finally-pledges-support-to-suadi-led-coalition-in-yemen-raxanreeb-online/ |archive-url=https://archive.today/20150407194428/http://www.wargeyska.so/somalia-somalia-finally-pledges-support-to-suadi-led-coalition-in-yemen-raxanreeb-online/ |url-status=dead |archive-date= 7 April 2015 |accessdate=7 April 2015 |agency=RBC Radio |date=7 April 2015}}</ref><ref name=\"FP 11-01-2016\">{{cite news|last=Ricks|first=Thomas E.|title=What Would a Saudi-Iran War Look Like? Don't look now, but it is already here|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2016/01/11/what-would-a-saudi-iran-war-look-like-dont-look-now-but-it-is-already-here/|accessdate=5 October 2016|work=[[Foreign Policy]]|date=11 January 2016}}</ref>\n| {{flag|Turkey|size=20px}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.turkiyegazetesi.com.tr/gundem/250295.aspx|title=D\u0131\u015fi\u015fleri Bakanl\u0131\u011f\u0131, Husi ter\u00f6r\u00fcne kar\u015f\u0131 Yemen'e destek verdi|accessdate=14 April 2017|work=T\u00fcrkiye|date=26 March 2013|language=tr}}</ref>\n| {{flag|United States|size=20px}}<ref>{{cite news|title=Breaking Yemen's Stalemate|url=https://worldview.stratfor.com/article/breaking-